======================================================================
                               CFJ 897

"The requirements in Rule 217 on Judgements apply to the
 determinations of the members of a Board of Appeal, as well as to
 the Judgements of Judges."

======================================================================

Judge:       Macross

Judgement:   TRUE

Eligible:    Andre, Blob, Chuck, elJefe, Harlequin, KoJen, Macross,
             Michael, Murphy, Oerjan, Steve, Swann, Vanyel, Zefram

